# Enable cross-origin isolation so SharedArrayBuffer is available. The
# app uses it for Pyodide's interrupt buffer, which lets the Stop button
# cancel a running train/infer cooperatively instead of nuking the worker.
#
# Syntax recognized by Netlify and Cloudflare Pages. On other hosts
# (Vercel, S3+CloudFront, plain nginx) the same two headers must be set
# via the host's native config — see vite.config.ts for the values.
/*
  Cross-Origin-Opener-Policy: same-origin
  Cross-Origin-Embedder-Policy: credentialless
